  "title": "Customer Service Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle customer appointments booking, incoming call &amp; register customers</li>\n  <li>Handle check out transactions on the computer system</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service and treatment recommendation to customers</li>\n  <li>Relationship building with existing and new customers to maximize sale opportunities</li>\n  <li>Handle customer problem and feedback</li>\n  <li>Deliver professional consultation and evaluation of customers’ needs</li>\n  <li>Follow up consultation with customers with regards to their treatments and products purchased</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Pleasant personality and have great patience</li>\n  <li>Able to handle counter system</li>\n  <li>Good in communication</li>\n  <li>Relevant work experience preferred</li>\n  <li>Must be able to work on weekends and public holidays</li>\n</ul>",
